            <div class="mb-6">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Our Solution:</h4>
              <p class="text-charcoal-600 dark:text-dark-text leading-relaxed font-medium">
                Optimized OBM system with enhanced lubricity + real-time rheology management + comprehensive hydraulics
                modeling.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-6">
              <div class="text-center p-5 bg-warm-white dark:bg-dark-bg-lighter rounded-xl shadow-soft">
                <div class="text-4xl font-black text-safety-orange mb-2 font-mono">60%</div>
                <div class="text-xs font-bold text-charcoal-600 dark:text-dark-text-muted uppercase tracking-wider">
